D2a — Add Log BP BU Resolution Summary (Compose)

Click the + between Loop BP Rows close and BP File Has Data → Add an action
Choose Data Operation → Compose
Rename via "..." → Rename:

Log BP BU Resolution Summary

Click into the Inputs field, switch to fx, paste:

concat('BP BU Resolution Summary — Resolved: ', string(variables('varBPOwningBUResolved')), ', Unmapped: ', string(variables('varBPOwningBUUnmapped')), ', Auto-Created Mapping: ', string(variables('varBPOwningBUAutoCreated')), ', Manual Override Skipped: ', string(variables('varBPOwningBUManualSkipped')), '. Total processed: ', string(add(add(add(variables('varBPOwningBUResolved'), variables('varBPOwningBUUnmapped')), variables('varBPOwningBUAutoCreated')), variables('varBPOwningBUManualSkipped'))), '.')

Click outside the field.

Sample output this will produce:
BP BU Resolution Summary — Resolved: 18, Unmapped: 3, Auto-Created Mapping: 2, Manual Override Skipped: 1. Total processed: 24.
Note the slight wording difference vs the App summary — Auto-Created Mapping (not Missing (no Org Unit)). The two sides have semantically different "third category": App's third counter is Missing (no source data), BP's third is AutoCreated (mapping row newly written this run). Wording matches semantics.

D2b — Add Append BP BU Summary to Warnings (Append to string variable)

Click the + between Log BP BU Resolution Summary and BP File Has Data → Add an action
Search Append to string variable → Variable → Append to string variable
Rename via "..." → Rename:

Append BP BU Summary to Warnings

Configure:

Name (dropdown):
varWarnings
Value — click into field, switch to fx, paste:
concat(if(empty(variables('varWarnings')), '', decodeUriComponent('%0A')), outputs('Log_BP_BU_Resolution_Summary'))
